        <title>RING GEAR AND PINION</title>
        <para>Ring Gear and Drive Pinion are matched parts and must be replaced in sets.</para>
        <para>To aid in identifying gear sets, both parts are stamped with such information as number of pinion and ring
            gear teeth, individual part number and matched set number (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f1401603">Figure 3</hotlnk>).
        </para>
